    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration enthusiasts! This vehicle is the ultimate project opportunity for someone looking to build something special from the ground up. While it is currently in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again, it offers a fantastic foundation for a complete transformation. If you have the tools and the passion, this is the perfect chance to save a classic and make it your own!",
