      "description": "We are pleased to present this vehicle in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This unit has been maintained to the highest standards, exhibiting no signs of wear and retaining its original aesthetic and mechanical integrity. A rare find for the serious enthusiast, this vehicle offers a pristine driving experience that mirrors its initial delivery. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
